{"tid":2126365,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【迷之武肺病人？】滙豐上水中心分行員工初步確診　即日起關閉14天","createTime":"2020-07-26T19:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T02:47:25.000Z","uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fb78bc60e72776c98d0c153d149325cb58d01f22","tid":2126365,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T19:09:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1539806_1_L_20200725112416.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1539806_1_L_20200725112416.jpg&h=58548d2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539806-20200725.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539806-20200725.htm&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qx%2F2u4%2BaHFFj7NdFJeB1nj9U%3D&h=77a864ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539806-20200725.htm&h=b5305eb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539806-20200725.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"violet\">2020-07-25 HKT 11:11</span></span></strong><br />\n滙豐銀行上水中心卓越理財中心有一名員工初步確診。（港台圖片）<br />\n<br />\n滙豐銀行上水中心卓越理財中心有一名員工初步確診感染新型冠狀病毒病，滙豐宣布，有關分行即日起暫停服務14天，並進行清潔及消毒，分行所有員工在家自我隔離最少14 天，亦會進行病毒檢測作為防預措施。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐表示，初步確診員工上星期五起開始在家工作，其後於本月22及23日到上水中心卓越理財中心上班，他的主要職責是在分行大堂解答客戶一般查詢，因此與客戶的緊密接觸有限，分行所有員工在當值期間都有戴上口罩，及每日進行體溫檢測。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已經係兩日前<br />\n我到而家仲未搵到佢個病人編號<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪我眼殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無人幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係銀行職員唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d293479668de95d463bc41d595fdaff9250f47f","tid":2126365,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T19:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fdf5bd2be8ad25d17e330bb7b18944cd86398c7","tid":2126365,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T19:11:57.000Z","msg":"全民停工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a8e820a5bf76e8cfba85a126d95f444c7be736","tid":2126365,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T19:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vKHhRmc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvKHhRmc.png&h=f21b4b90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上水中心吉既屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9669daa6358d88b54363e21ddf057249d4885673","tid":2126365,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a127daf20c422090ca7f738b4389faf0873f44da","tid":2126365,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"39a8e820a5bf76e8cfba85a126d95f444c7be736","tid":2126365,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T19:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vKHhRmc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvKHhRmc.png&h=f21b4b90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上水中心吉既屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}